{"tid":808230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士上嚴禁飲食啊屌你","createTime":"2018-09-06T07:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T10:49:42.000Z","uid":137940,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e49ae2ad00271ebb16ea6c0f477fc80b978fbaac","tid":808230,"uid":137940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"其實見到啲人搭巴士食野飲野都已經唔會理佢地，反正又影響唔到我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係可唔可以唔好食咁撚大陣味嘅野食呢？食乜撚嘢榴槤乜叉乜叉，成陣榴槤味沖撚哂出黎， 驚死全車人都唔撚知你食緊榴槤咩，搞到成架車臭撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有啲乜尻印尼撈麵，又係成陣味沖哂出黎，真係屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 理下其他人嘅感受得唔撚得，唔撚係全部人都鐘意聞到呢啲味架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8329a8721a6f0c9b7f5a4c11a6f1d9e05c0e2992","tid":808230,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"有無當面屌柒佢？"},{"pid":"0b1e0397fae937c8c6f40667babfc30dd8922026","tid":808230,"uid":137940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8329a8721a6f0c9b7f5a4c11a6f1d9e05c0e2992","tid":808230,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"有無當面屌柒佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"梗係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次趕尻埋佢地啲仆街落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738c7d4ddb542dd681590fdeff8e3941d03eddc7","tid":808230,"uid":134747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"榴槤都唔食得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"h